urfaced—the system is operating normally.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"\\nComparing current state (05:53 UTC) vs heartbeat-state.json (05:18 UTC):\\n\\n**Active sessions comparison:**\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` — still running ✅\\n- `cron:e7885813` — still running ✅\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` — still running ✅\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` — idle but intact ✅\\n\\nAll three active crons unchanged. No new failures. No new sessions. No blockers surfaced.\\n\\nPipeline stable. Nothing changed.\\n\\n**SILENT.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 29130,\n            \"output\": 590,\n            \"totalTokens\": 44094,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 430,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776232456992,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e5b0a1849e44cc84ec41e12582ae8\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"33faeee0\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776232126814,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 41231,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\"